The paper deals with anomaly detection in large-scale data processing systems, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed algorithm involves the use of statistical estimators and locality-sensitive hashing, which are common techniques in data structures (cs.DS) and cryptography (cs.CR).
